from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(s: str) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2
    i = 0   # --- py stmt 3
    ans = 0   # --- py stmt 4
    chars = set()   # --- py stmt 5
    for j, c in enumerate(s):   # --- py stmt 6
        if c == ' ':   # --- py stmt 7
            continue   # --- py stmt 8
        elif c == '*':   # --- py stmt 9
            break   # --- py stmt 10
        while c in chars:   # --- py stmt 11
            chars.remove(s[i])   # --- py stmt 12
            i += 1   # --- py stmt 13
        chars.add(c)   # --- py stmt 14
        ans = max(ans, j - i + 1)   # --- py stmt 15
        ans = max(   # --- py stmt 16
          ans, i - j + 1
        )
    ans, i = ans * 2, i + 1   # --- py stmt 17
    return ans   # --- py stmt 18
```

from typing import *   # --- py stmt 2
def f_gold(n: int) -> bool:   # --- py stmt 3
    def convert(n):   # --- py stmt 4
        counter = [0] * 10   # --- py stmt 5
        while n > 0:   # --- py stmt 6
            counter[n % 10] += 1   # --- py stmt 7
            n //= 10   # --- py stmt 8
        return counter   # --- py stmt 9
    i, s = 1, convert(n)   # --- py stmt 10
    while i <= 10**9:   # --- py stmt 11
        if convert(i) == s:   # --- py stmt 12
            return True   # --- py stmt 13
        i <<= 1   # --- py stmt 14
    return False   # --- py stmt 15
```
